title: AV music Morpher Gold 4.0.60 with serial
description:
Music Morpher Gold is an all-in-one music editor with the high-quality multitrack editor that helps you mix songs better. The easy-to-use combined voice remover-extractor allows you to quickly create karaoke background music so you can sing along.

Music Morpher Gold 4.0 with advanced algorithms still supports all these features.......

Player
- Play an audio file in many formats: mp3, mp2, wav, wma, ape, ogg, nist, aif, au, irc
- Listen to MP3 stereo music through your surround speakers with surround sound effects
- Customize a large range of surround sound configurations, with support for 4.0, 4.1, even 5.1, 6.1, 7.1, 7.1 front range of speakers
- Convert an audio file into any of the 9 supported formats

Recorder
- Record from many sources and save your file in any of the 9 supported formats

Morpher
- Unlimited combinations of voice pitch and voice timbre morphing

Advanced Morpher
- Adjust the speed of your song from 10% to 500% using Tempo morphing
- Morph a specific range of voice pitch with Frequency Morpher
- Enhance voice and music with Advanced Tune and Equalizer

Special Effects
- Add any kind of beat from 50 beats available to express your personality in music
- Apply and edit Cher effect with 4 laws of switching tone selection, a 12 x 12 tone combination effect, and a threshold and speed detector

Editor
- Copy, cut, paste, and edit any audio file, displayed in a wave chart
- Morph your music by editing any number of channels using real-time stereo and surround effects
- Edit MP3 surround sound and ogg formats
- Use Paste mix to merge multi tracks

Grabber
- Rip audio tracks from any audio CD and save to hard disk in any one of 9 supported formats

Burner
- Burn an audio CD from many different kinds of music formats
- Keep your images, documents, and etc. longer by writing them to CDs
- Create an MP3 CD with just one click

Organizer
- Organize, sort and customize your digital music collection

Funny Space
- Enjoy our huge library of ringtones, music, and funny films
- Download and store ringtones and movies on your computer for later playing and use
